title: A.S. Jeunes Tahitiens
text:
Association Sportive Jeunes Tahitienes, is a <a href="association%20football">football</a> club from <a href="Papeete">Papeete</a>, <a href="Tahiti">Tahiti</a>. It's one of the oldest football clubs in <a href="French%20Polynesia">French Polynesia</a>, been founded on 1923. It currently competes at <a href="Tahiti%20Ligue%201">Tahiti Ligue 1</a>, after being promoted from <a href="Tahiti%20Ligue%202">Tahiti Ligue 2</a> in the 2017–18 season.
